%% Data Flow Diagram - Llama Stack Distribution
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Milvus as Milvus<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    participant FMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Inference Request (vLLM Backend)

    Client->>LS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP<br/>Auth: None (platform-managed)
    LS->>vLLM: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: API Token (VLLM_API_TOKEN)
    vLLM-->>LS: Inference response
    LS->>PG: Store session/state<br/>PostgreSQL 5432/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>LS: Acknowledged
    LS-->>Client: Chat completion response

    Note over Client,Milvus: Flow 2: RAG Query (Vector Search + Inference)

    Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP<br/>RAG query
    LS->>Milvus: Vector similarity search<br/>gRPC/HTTP<br/>Auth: Token (MILVUS_TOKEN)
    Milvus-->>LS: Relevant document chunks
    LS->>vLLM: Augmented inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: API Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Generated response
    LS->>PG: Persist state<br/>5432/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    PG-->>LS: Acknowledged
    LS-->>Client: RAG response

    Note over Client,FMS: Flow 3: Safety-Guarded Inference

    Client->>LS: POST /v1/inference/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP<br/>With safety enabled
    LS->>FMS: Safety check (input)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: None
    FMS-->>LS: Safety verdict
    alt Input is safe
        LS->>vLLM: Forward inference<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: API Token
        vLLM-->>LS: Inference response
        LS->>FMS: Safety check (output)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        FMS-->>LS: Safety verdict
        LS-->>Client: Guarded response
    else Input is unsafe
        LS-->>Client: Safety violation response
    end
